Problem ;
Local game shop owner is requesting a game that is;
1. entirely text based.
2. can record the time played 
3. can record the player's name and score

Solution; 
Game topic :

software : python

Design statement:
I will to design and make a text-based rpg game for a client who is a current game shop owner. 
The rpg will be made in the ———— and is constructed using the software python on mac processor. 
It will take  4 weeks to make and will be evaluated according to the following criteria ;

 - The program will be completely text based
 - the program will be able to record the total amount of play time
 - the program will record the playe's name
 - the program will record the player's score in-game in real time
 - Interface written in english
 - The program will be able to pause mid-game and resume
 - The program will be able to emit sound accomodated to gameplay
 - the program will have check-points in order to save progress made by player
 - The program will have different story outcomes depending on player's in-game decisions
 - The program will be downloadable via online sources
